faqs.question: How do I apply?
faqs.answer: Visit our application page and complete the online form. Our admissions team will guide you through the process.

faqs.question: What programs are available?
faqs.answer: CSU offers over 50 online degree programs including business, criminal justice, fire science, and more.

faqs.question: How much is tuition?
faqs.answer: Tuition varies by program. Partner employees receive exclusive discounts on all programs.

faqs.question: Is financial aid available?
faqs.answer: Yes! CSU offers various financial aid options including federal aid, military benefits, and payment plans.
